             was indicted for <rs id="t18321129-203-off1141" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18321129-203-off1141" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18321129-203-off1141" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18321129-203-cd1142" type="crimeDate">9th of November</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18321129-203-off1141 t18321129-203-cd1142"></join>, 3 pairs of shoes, value 7s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
